```

&lt;div class="lecture-selection"&gt;
    &lt;span style="font-weight: 700"&gt;C&lt;/span&gt;
    &lt;a style="padding-left: 0.8em"&gt;정지원&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;span style="padding-left: 10em; font-size:0.9em"&gt;+&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

```이 부분을 CSS selector를 써서 구현하는 건 어떨까요?
```
.lecture-selection span:first-child {font-weight: 700}
.lecture-selection a {padding-left: 0.8em}
.lecture-selection span {padding-left: 10em; font-size:0.9em}
```
이런 식으로요.
